This then is Chriſtianity, that we wiſh well to all Mankind, and are content with our own

Condition; that we ſympathize with our Neighbour, as Members one of another;
               Rom. 12. that we Rejoyce with them that do Rejoyce, and Mourn with them that Mourn; that we be not high-minded, but apt to preferr one another in Honour: that we think no Evil, that we ſpeak no Evil of any Man; but that we walk according to the Goſpel, and not in Strife and Envying.
